---
title: Tex Mex Steak Tortillas with Sweet Potato Wedges and Garlic Mayo
description: What do you think of when you think of steak? Steak and chips? Steak with pepper sauce? Well, we want to push the steak boundaries and we're pretty sure we are with our luxuriously tasty steak tortillas. You can smother them with garlicky mayo and our scrumptious salad and enjoy with some delightful sweet potato chips.
